@startuml Authentication_Flow_State_Machine

title "Authentication Flow State Machine Diagram\nEnterprise Staffing System (ESS)"

skinparam defaultFontName "Serif"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam titleFontSize 16
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
    RoundCorner 8
}

[*] --> LoginPage

state "Login Page" as LoginPage
state "Firebase Authentication" as FirebaseAuth
state "Approval Check" as ApprovalCheck
state "MFA Check" as MFACheck
state "MFA Setup\n(First Time)" as MFASetup
state "MFA Verify\n(TOTP Code)" as MFAVerify
state "Role-Based\nDashboard Redirect" as Dashboard
state "Access Denied" as Denied

LoginPage : CAPTCHA + Rate Limiting
LoginPage : (5 attempts / 2-min lockout)

LoginPage --> FirebaseAuth : Submit

FirebaseAuth : Email + Password
FirebaseAuth : Google Sign-In
FirebaseAuth : Phone OTP

FirebaseAuth --> ApprovalCheck : auth success
FirebaseAuth --> LoginPage : auth failed

ApprovalCheck : approvalStatus checked
ApprovalCheck : pending / approved / rejected

ApprovalCheck --> Denied : pending or rejected
ApprovalCheck --> MFACheck : approved

Denied : "Awaiting approval from\nAdmin or Area HR"
Denied --> [*] : forced sign-out

MFACheck : MFA required for:\nadmin, hr, general_manager,\nsupervisor, project_manager

MFACheck --> MFASetup : MFA role +\nnot yet enabled
MFACheck --> MFAVerify : MFA role +\nalready enabled
MFACheck --> Dashboard : non-MFA role

MFASetup : Scan QR code with\nGoogle Authenticator
MFASetup --> Dashboard : setup complete

MFAVerify : Enter 6-digit TOTP code\n(5 attempts max)
MFAVerify --> Dashboard : code valid
MFAVerify --> LoginPage : 5 failed → logout

Dashboard --> [*] : admin → /admin/dashboard\nhr → /hr/dashboard\ngm → /manager/dashboard\npm → /pm/dashboard\nsupervisor → /supervisor/dashboard\nemployee → /employee/dashboard\nintern → /intern/dashboard

@enduml
